Author: bharath
Content: Dubai is run by folks with vision. Folks who realize that oil is a finite, non-renewable resource and they need to spend their petrodollars preparing for the day that it runs out. Apparently, its quite the tourist destination. Indoor skiing, snorkeling and duty free shopping just a 4 hr flight from Frankfurt.
